genresAdvancedInfo.name: kashmiri pop
genresAdvancedInfo.description: Kashmiri pop is a contemporary music genre that emerged in the 1990s, featuring catchy melodies and upbeat rhythms. It draws inspiration from Bollywood and Western pop music, with lyrics often focusing on love and relationships. The genre has become a staple of the music industry in Kashmir, with many popular artists hailing from the region.
